Alex Cross;;2012;;PG-13;;Action,Crime,Mystery;;5.2;;Rob Cohen;;Tyler Perry,Matthew Fox,Rachel Nichols,Edward Burns,Jean Reno,Carmen Ejogo,Cicely Tyson,John C. McGinley,Werner Daehn,Yara Shahidi,Sayeed Shahidi,Bonnie Bentley,Stephany Jacobsen,Giancarlo Esposito,Chad Lindberg,Simenona Martinez,Jessalyn Wanlim,Christian Mathis;;Washington DC detective Alex Cross goes up against the hitman 'Picasso'. As Alex investigates Picasso's gruesome murders, Picasso decides to send him a message by killing his wife. Enraged, Cross vows to hunt down the killer, if it's the last thing he does. However, Picasso is a mastermind and continues to evade Cross while pushing him to an ethical breaking point as a cop and a father. As Cross closes in on the killer, he discovers evidence that points to the unimaginable - a revelation that can change everything.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1712170/